Date: Tue, 23 Mar 2010 15:31:27 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 5/5] Add DS1339 RTC device node for fsl_p2020 DS board.

There are two RTC devices on fsl_p2020DS board, one(rtc_cmos)
is on ISA bus using i8259 interrupt controller, the other(ds1339)
is on I2C-1 bus.

Signed-off-by: Andrew Liu <shengping.liu@windriver.com>
---
 arch/powerpc/boot/dts/p2020ds.dts |    5 +++++
 1 files changed, 5 insertions(+), 0 deletions(-)

diff --git a/arch/powerpc/boot/dts/p2020ds.dts b/arch/powerpc/boot/dts/p2020ds.dts
index 67dfbd6..14b6ff6 100644
--- a/arch/powerpc/boot/dts/p2020ds.dts
+++ b/arch/powerpc/boot/dts/p2020ds.dts
@@ -215,6 +215,11 @@
 			interrupts = <43 2>;
 			interrupt-parent = <&mpic>;
 			dfsrr;
+
+			rtc@68 {
+				compatible = "dallas,ds1339";
+				reg = <0x68>;
+			};
 		};
 
 		serial0: serial@4500 {
